sponser-logo-wrap"><img loading="lazy" src="/69816f59b713f65ad8e4f653/69816fe6414bd741b0035e38_S.SENS logo final-13 2.png" alt="" class="project-sponser-logo"/></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section testimonial"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-4 w-container"><div class="testimonial-for-desktop"><div class="testimonial-header"><div class="overflow-hidden"><div class="centered-header"><h2 class="sub-heading">Phản hồi từ khách hàng</h2></div></div></div><div class="testimonials-wrap"><div class="testimonial-5"><div class="testimonial-wrap"><div class="rating-star-wrap"><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f9baeb25e33dacb5ed570f_material-symbols_star.svg" alt="" class="rating-star"/><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f9baeb25e33dacb5ed570f_material-symbols_star.svg" alt="" class="rating-star"/><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f9baeb25e33dacb5ed570f_material-symbols_star.svg" alt="Star Icon" class="rating-star"/><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f9baeb25e33dacb5ed570f_material-symbols_star.svg" alt="" class="rating-star"/><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f9baeb25e33dacb5ed570f_material-symbols_star.svg" alt="" class="rating-star"/></div><div class="testimonial-content-wrap"><div class="testimonial-content-1">“Website chạm đúng đến giá trị cốt lõi của thương hiệu từ màu sắc, bố cục đến nội dung. Team S.Sens rất hài lòng khi nhận được sản phẩm cũng như cách làm việc của studio”</div></div><div class="testimonial-user-wrap"><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f976b821e73c080de304e3_Ellipse 3 (1).svg" alt="" class="testimonal-user-img"/><div class="testimonial-user-name-tag"><div class="testimonial-user-name">Thu Hang</div><p class="para-2">S.Sens Homes - Founder</p></div></div></div></div><div class="testimonial-8"><div class="testimonial-wrap"><div class="rating-star-wrap"><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f9baeb25e33dacb5ed570f_material-symbols_star.svg" alt="" class="rating-star"/><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f9baeb25e33dacb5ed570f_material-symbols_star.svg" alt="" class="rating-star"/><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f9baeb25e33dacb5ed570f_material-symbols_star.svg" alt="" class="rating-star"/><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f9baeb25e33dacb5ed570f_material-symbols_star.svg" alt="" class="rating-star"/><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f9baeb25e33dacb5ed570f_material-symbols_star.svg" alt="" class="rating-star"/></div><div class="testimonial-content-wrap"><div class="testimonial-content-1">“Đã từng có cơ hội làm việc với Dao.Design và rất hài lòng về sự chỉn chu trong giao tiếp cũng như chuyên môn thiết kế của studio&quot; </div></div><div class="testimonial-user-wrap"><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f976b821e73c080de304e4_Ellipse 3 (2).svg" alt="" class="testimonal-user-img"/><div class="testimonial-user-name-tag"><div class="div-block-85"><div class="testimonial-user-name">Long Nguyen</div><a data-wf-native-id-path="d86e2007-b096-1578-144f-df220c402008" data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-element-id="d86e2007-b096-1578-144f-df220c402008" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/longnc/" target="_blank" class="w-inline-block"><img src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69805dedda39368fe35fee07_pixelarticons_external-link.png" loading="lazy" alt="" class="image-10"/></a></div><p class="para-2">The Martec - Tech Lead</p></div></div></div></div><div class="testimonial-7"><div class="testimonial-wrap"><div class="rating-star-wrap"><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f9baeb25e33dacb5ed570f_material-symbols_star.svg" alt="" class="rating-star"/><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f9baeb25e33dacb5ed570f_material-symbols_star.svg" alt="" class="rating-star"/><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f9baeb25e33dacb5ed570f_material-symbols_star.svg" alt="" class="rating-star"/><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f9baeb25e33dacb5ed570f_material-symbols_star.svg" alt="" class="rating-star"/><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f9baeb25e33dacb5ed570f_material-symbols_star.svg" alt="" class="rating-star"/></div><div class="testimonial-content-wrap"><div class="testimonial-content-1">“One of those guys i know off don’t need the best equipment, a piece of paper can draw a landscape of awesomeness to impress the crowd.”</div></div><div class="testimonial-user-wrap"><img loading="lazy" src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69f976b821e73c080de304e5_Ellipse 3 (3).svg" alt="" class="testimonal-user-img"/><div class="testimonial-user-name-tag"><div class="div-block-85"><div class="testimonial-user-name">Joe Zhou</div><a data-wf-native-id-path="ce831001-e151-3a81-8924-10b0a38498ce" data-wf-ao-click-engagement-tracking="true" data-wf-element-id="ce831001-e151-3a81-8924-10b0a38498ce" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/joehz/?lipi=urn%3Ali%3Apage%3Ad_flagship3_search_srp_all%3BWRfrGP3MQNK06U8ia1%2BAqQ%3D%3D" target="_blank" class="w-inline-block"><img src="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69805dedda39368fe35fee07_pixelarticons_external-link.png" loading="lazy" alt="" class="image-10"/></a></div><p class="para-2">The Martec - CTO</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class="sticky"><section data-w-id="112bebe6-0843-ff3d-2ac4-b864ab8cc9e1" class="section big-image display-desktop"><div class="big-img-fixed-2"><div data-poster-url="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69ac052d1fc1d63b543c234f_Hero video_poster.0000000.jpg" data-video-urls="/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69ac052d1fc1d63b543c234f_Hero video_mp4.mp4,/696db0cd2780ac54df960dfb/69ac052d1fc1d63b543c234f_Hero video_webm.webm" data-autoplay="true" data-loop="true" data-wf-ignore="true" class="background-video-23 w-background-video w-background-video-atom"><video id="1ff26172-5e9d-c471-0ef6-3e77a133a10d-video"